Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.89,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,521)}今天也一如往常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:17.66,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}但是不知为何
