Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:24.44,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}弄脏的衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.42,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}沾染上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:30.37,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}这自欺欺人的谎言…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:35.50,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,348)}我到底在保护什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.92,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}不畏失去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:43.63,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}即便长大成人 也心怀梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.63,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}因为我只希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:48.15,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}自己能将这些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:51.05,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,351)}视为骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:55.10,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}吐出来 舍弃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.98,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.73,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,347)}回忆起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.65,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:05.61,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,980)}希望明天我能这样说
